"acd70f32ba60d614340999990e238b8782ab4449","tid":1448113,"uid":33543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQZURP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQZURP7.jpg&h=e8ff53ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvexDu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvexDu8.jpg&h=6025e5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnQpuBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnQpuBP.jpg&h=bdc91acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Product should only be used outdoors. <br />\n<br />\nDo not fire directly at personnel</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記者會上話會跟足廠商指引而無必要親身試彈，宜家冇跟指引就有必要親身試啦？</span><br />\n<br />\n間廠叫NonLethal Technology, 有冇人去提醒下間廠再培訓垃圾狗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nonlethaltechnologies.com%2F&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=deb38b48\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n去信Nonlethal Technologies投訴香港警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447918</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f84c6cb09b02ea72340fff54c2dbeeff45ea89f7","tid":1448113,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:42.000Z","msg":"721 811 香港警察 殺人放火"},{"pid":"9075ce04b34a73f630f648f47b410a833d419c1a","tid":1448113,"uid":259592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:31:40.000Z","msg":"721 811 香港警察 殺人放火"},{"pid":"e73598cb9bb6cfe7df5bf746d0e180b5276a0477","tid":1448113,"uid":286651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:31:49.000Z","msg":"721 811 香港警察 殺人放火"},{"pid":"4b2371bed5cd9bb1f4be4506d8